s Imane Khelif, won her fight in just 46 seconds after her opponent admitted defeat and walked off the ring while crying and in pain.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boxing world\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"another fighter\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"her fight\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's opponent, Angela Carini of Italy, stated after the fight that she had \\\"never been hit so hard in my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9545060863419533, \"rank\": 0.03852295794576427, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's opponent\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian fighter went viral online as social media users speculated that she was actually a man due to the fighter's body and facial features as well as the fact that she did not pass last year's gender test.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http